<table
  align="center"
  width="100%"
  border="0"
  cellpadding="0"
  cellspacing="0"
  role="presentation"
  style="padding: 0px 35px 25px 35px"
>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td>
        <p
          style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:24px 0 0 0;color:#333;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, &#x27;Roboto&#x27;, &#x27;Oxygen&#x27;, &#x27;Ubuntu&#x27;, &#x27;Cantarell&#x27;, &#x27;Fira Sans&#x27;, &#x27;Droid Sans&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, sans-serif;"
        >
          Hello
          {{restaurantName}}
          team,
        </p>
        <p
          style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:24px 0;color:#2947C2;font-weight: bold;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, &#x27;Roboto&#x27;, &#x27;Oxygen&#x27;, &#x27;Ubuntu&#x27;, &#x27;Cantarell&#x27;, &#x27;Fira Sans&#x27;, &#x27;Droid Sans&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px"
        >
          ⚠️ Deployment Failed! There was an issue publishing your website
          updates.
        </p>

        <div
          style="
                                background-color: #ffebee;
                                border-radius: 8px;
                                padding: 16px 20px;
                                margin: 20px 0;
                                border: 1px solid #ffcdd2;
                                font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, &#x27;Roboto&#x27;, &#x27;Oxygen&#x27;, &#x27;Ubuntu&#x27;, &#x27;Cantarell&#x27;, &#x27;Fira Sans&#x27;, &#x27;Droid Sans&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, sans-serif;"
        >
          <h3
            style="
                                  font-size: 16px; 
                                  margin: 0 0 12px 0; 
                                  font-weight: 600;
                                  font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, &#x27;Roboto&#x27;, sans-serif;"
          >
            Error Details
          </h3>
          <table
            width="100%"
            style="
                                  font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, &#x27;Roboto&#x27;, sans-serif;
                                  border-collapse: separate;
                                  border-spacing: 0 8px;
                                "
          >
            <tr>
              <td
                style="
                                      color: #5f6b7a;
                                      font-weight: 500;
                                      width: 40%;
                                      font-size: 14px;
                                      padding-right: 10px;
                                    "
              >
                Error Message:
              </td>
              <td
                style="
                                      color: #222222;
                                      font-weight: 600;
                                      font-size: 14px;
                                    "
              >
                {{errorMessage}}
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td
                style="
                                      color: #5f6b7a;
                                      font-weight: 500;
                                      width: 40%;
                                      font-size: 14px;
                                      padding-right: 10px;
                                    "
              >
                Attempted Deployment Time:
              </td>
              <td
                style="
                                      color: #222222;
                                      font-weight: 600;
                                      font-size: 14px;
                                    "
              >
                {{deploymentTime}}
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td
                style="
                                      color: #5f6b7a;
                                      font-weight: 500;
                                      width: 40%;
                                      font-size: 14px;
                                      padding-right: 10px;
                                    "
              >
                Deployment Initiated By:
              </td>
              <td
                style="
                                      color: #222222;
                                      font-weight: 600;
                                      font-size: 14px;
                                    "
              >
                {{deployedBy}}
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </div>
        <p
          style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:24px 0 0 0;color:#333;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, &#x27;Roboto&#x27;, &#x27;Oxygen&#x27;, &#x27;Ubuntu&#x27;, &#x27;Cantarell&#x27;, &#x27;Fira Sans&#x27;, &#x27;Droid Sans&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, sans-serif;"
        >
          Please try again after some time. If the isues still persists, please
          reach out to us at
          <a
            href="mailto:support@choosepos.com"
            style="color:#2947C2;text-decoration-line:none;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, &#x27;Roboto&#x27;, &#x27;Oxygen&#x27;, &#x27;Ubuntu&#x27;, &#x27;Cantarell&#x27;, &#x27;Fira Sans&#x27;, &#x27;Droid Sans&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, sans-serif;text-decoration:underline"
            target="_blank"
          >support@choosepos.com</a>.
        </p>

        <p
          style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;margin:24px 0 0 0;color:#333;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, &#x27;Roboto&#x27;, &#x27;Oxygen&#x27;, &#x27;Ubuntu&#x27;, &#x27;Cantarell&#x27;, &#x27;Fira Sans&#x27;, &#x27;Droid Sans&#x27;, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, sans-serif;"
        >
          Best regards,<br />Choose Team
        </p>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>